snippet.title: Castle Crashers DLC Update | Wishlist Today!
snippet.description:
Castle Crashers Painter Boss Paradise DLC is now available for wishlisting on Steam! Join us in this development update video as we go over new information while playing against the Frost King on level 5.

The Painter Boss Paradise DLC will launch EARLY SUMMER 2025 on Steam for $3.99!

You can wishlist the game on Steam RIGHT NOW--it's the best way to support us!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3133920/Castle_Crashers__Painters_Boss_Paradise/

As promised in the video, here are links to follow us:
🥚 https://links.thebehemoth.com/
🥚Subscribe to us on YouTube by clicking the button above
🥚 https://www.twitch.tv/thebehemoth
🥚 https://beh.gg/news

*Regional pricing subject to adjustments
